clusterList.phrase: do you remember how angry with me you became when i called you an abrek and described your beliefs as a sort of abreki catechism you said that all men should be made so and that the abandonment of the self and the renunciation of personal needs and desires all feelings attachments and links should be a normal state the everyday condition of all humanity out of that cruel renunciation and extreme fanaticism you now want to make a general principle applicable to the whole community you want crazy things impossible things the total negation of nature man and society
